---
title: Apricot Miso Chicken with Chili Lime Broccoli & Ginger Rice
description: Our chefs are always brainstorming ways to make “chicken for dinner” a little more awesome. The delicious upgrade this week: a glossy apricot jam, miso, and lime-spiked pan sauce. Sweet and savory is the name of the game here, with the sides being no exception. Crispy roasted broccoli tossed with lime zest and chili flakes and ginger-scented rice pair perfectly with the saucy chicken. Get ready for a flavor explosion.
